snippet.title: Musician on a Mission
snippet.description:
Want your music to sound professional?

You're in the right place.

On this channel, you will learn how to record studio level tracks in a home studio...

And how to mix music like a pro.

You'll learn about:
- Songwriting
- Home recording
- Mixing
- Recording vocals and mixing vocals
- Mixing with EQ
- Mixing with compression
- And everything else you need to know about making music at home

I want to help you be more creative. I want to help you get your music out there…

So YOU can have an impact. So YOU can get the appreciation you deserve.

You have the ability to produce great music and share it with the world - regardless of your situation.

So, subscribe now for weekly videos, and start making music that sounds radio ready.

- Rob Mayzes (Founder of Musician on a Mission)
